lack/80 font-medium\">Independent AC Units</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Card 3: Small Image (Double-Bezel) */}\n          <div className=\"md:col-span-1 md:row-span-1 bg-white/5 p-2 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10\">\n            <div className=\"relative h-full min-h-[300px] bg-[var(--surface-color)] rounded-[calc(2.5rem-0.5rem)] overflow-hidden group shadow-[inset_0_1px_1px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/molos.jpeg\" alt=\"Molos Area\" className=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:scale-[1.05] transition-transform duration-[1.5s] ease-[cubic-bezier(0.32,0.72,0,1)] mix-blend-luminosity grayscale\" />\n              <div className=\"absolute inset-0 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end bg-black/50\">\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-white/60 mb-2 font-medium\">03 / Taste</span>\n                <p className=\"text-base text-white\">Barista Station</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Card 4: Wide Feature (Double-Bezel) */}\n          <div className=\"md:col-span-2 md:row-span-1 bg-white/5 p-2 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10 group hover:border-[var(--accent-secondary)] transition-colors duration-700\">\n            <div className=\"h-full bg-[var(--surface-color)] rounded-[calc(2.5rem-0.5rem)] p-8 flex items-center shadow-[inset_0_1px_1px_rgba(255,255,255,0.05)]\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--accent-secondary)] mb-4 block font-medium\">04 / Privacy</span>\n                <p className=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white/90 font-light leading-[1.4]\">\n                  Noise-cancelling windows and advanced water filtration create an isolated environment.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* M